item.title: Laugh at the newbie
item.dc:creator: @arraness14 arraness14
item.description:
@arraness14 wrote:

jme_009:

[quote author=moparisthebest link=topic=2992.msg30384#msg30384 date=1147655948]
[quote author=jme_009 link=topic=2992.msg30305#msg30305 date=1147650053]
My ISP has blocked port 6667, how lame is that? They have blocked just about every useful port on me(They even said they did) and yet my friends who have the exact same plan as me dont have blocked ports. Wtf is up with that?

I wouldnt pay for an isp that blocked my ports at all
[/quote]

Sympatico sucks They really hate me ever since we got the unlimited bandwidth plan

Anyways, they said it looks like an "error" on their side, but then why am I the only one effected by it? It's the only high speed plan I can get where I live though. It better get fixed though, I can't stand the 2 hour waiting periods on the phone.

When I first phoned them, they said its not their fault, contact Linksys. I call linksys, and they tell me to contact MY ISP. It goes in circles, and that's not the first timeit's happened.

When I asked them about port 443, they kept chaning the subject. I should have been a bit more agressive.[/quote]

I have sympatico too..I never went on the IRC...becasue the few times I tried it didint work....we are gettong Rogers soon
